<!DOCTYPE html> <html lang="pt-BR"> <head> <meta charset="UTF-8"> <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"> <title>ArcadeX</title> <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Press+Start+2P&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"> <style> *{ margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; } body{ font-family:'Trebuchet MS', Arial, sans-serif; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0D0D0D,#1A1A2E); color:white; text-align:center; } header{ background:#8A2BE2; padding:20px; box-shadow:0 0 20px #8A2BE2; } header h1{ font-family:'Press Start 2P', cursive; font-size:2rem; text-shadow:0 0 10px white; } .hero{ padding:100px 20px; } .hero h2{ font-size:2.5rem; margin-bottom:20px; text-shadow:0 0 10px #8A2BE2; } .hero p{ font-size:1.2rem; color:#d0d0d0; max-width:600px; margin:0 auto 30px; } button{ background:#00BFFF; color:white; border:none; padding:15px 30px; border-radius:8px; cursor:pointer; font-size:1rem; box-shadow:0 0 15px #00BFFF; transition:0.3s; } button:hover{ transform:scale(1.05); box-shadow:0 0 25px #00BFFF; } footer{ padding:20px; background:#111; margin-top:50px; color:#999; } </style> </head> <body> <header> <h1>ArcadeX</h1> </header> <section class="hero"> <h2>Bem-vindo ao ArcadeX</h2> <p> Descubra jogos incríveis, desafios emocionantes e a melhor experiência gamer em um só lugar. </p> <button onclick="alert('Bem-vindo ao ArcadeX!')"> Começar </button> </section> <footer> © 2026 ArcadeX - Todos os direitos reservados </footer> </body> </html>
